    info_hrtss_workout: '**hrTSS (HR Training Stress Score)**\nTraining stress relative to your lactate threshold HR.\n100 = 1 hour at threshold effort.\n\n[dot:#82aaff] < 40 — Easy\n[dot:#ffc777] 40–80 — Moderate\n[dot:#ff966c] 80–120 — Threshold\n[dot:#ff5370] 120+ — Hard\n\nComparable across swim/bike/run — same scale.',
